<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：红黑树通过颜色约束维持近似平衡保证O(log n)操作，B+树通过多叉结构降低磁盘IO成为数据库索引首选，跳表用概率平衡替代严格平衡实现简单高效的并发有序结构。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="红黑树b树跳表分别通过颜色约束多叉节点和概率层级三种不同机制实现高效查找">红黑树、B+树、跳表分别通过颜色约束、多叉节点和概率层级三种不同机制实现高效查找</h2>
<h3 id="红黑树近似平衡的二叉搜索树">红黑树：近似平衡的二叉搜索树</h3>
<p><strong>红黑树的五条性质</strong>：</p>
<ol>
<li>节点是红色或黑色</li>
<li>根节点是黑色</li>
<li>所有叶子（NIL）是黑色</li>
<li>红色节点的子节点必须是黑色（不能有两个连续红色）</li>
<li>从任一节点到其叶子的所有路径包含相同数目的黑色节点</li>
</ol>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">性质5的推论：最长路径不超过最短路径的2倍
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">最短路径：全黑节点        最长路径：红黑交替
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    B                       B
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   / \                     / \
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  B   B                   R   B
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"> / \                     / \   \
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">B   B                   B   R   B
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                            /
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                           B
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">黑高=3，最短路径3，最长路径5（不超过2倍）</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>红黑树的平衡调整</strong>：</p>
